content: Na Hye-seok Street, the representative of female artists. It's a pity, but now it's just downtown Suwon.
Na Hye-seok Street is a real restaurant in Heaven. You can eat lunch, dessert, and dinner. If you can solve everything in a day, you can go back to the nearby Hyowon Gong ㅈ
It's great for eating or drinking with acquaintances. It's a lively street until late at night. It doesn't take long to see it soon
There is nothing to think about or go to restaurants and busking streets on weekends.
Millal School, an art museum run by the Christian Milal Foundation!! There are many more works and good exhibits than I thought
The art exhibits here are really personalized and charming. Not many people, the atmosphere is quite good.
